Coding Exercise 14: Distance Traveled

Use the 'reduce' helper to find the sum of all the distances traveled. Assign the result to the variable
'totalDistance'

var trips = [{ distance: 34 }, { distance: 12 } , { distance: 1 }];


// var totalDistance = trips.reduce(function(acum, trip) {
//     return acum + trip.distance;
// }, 0);

//My best solution

var totalDistance = trips.reduce((acum, trip) => acum + trip.distance, 0);




